And I remember what you said:

153
00:11:02,413 --> 00:11:06,611
"仅仅是因为我们做自己所做的 并不意味着我们必须孤独"
"Just because we do what we do doesn't mean we have to be lonely."

154
00:11:08,373 --> 00:11:10,603
我羡慕你可以那样说
I admired you for saying that.

155
00:11:14,293 --> 00:11:16,648
你准备给他们几个说吗?
Are you going to tell the others?

156
00:11:17,213 --> 00:11:19,602
她在那里会得到最好的照顾的 Ash...
She's going to get the best care there is,Ash...

157
00:11:19,693 --> 00:11:22,332
那也意味着我们将需要一大笔钱
which means we're going to need a lot of money.

158
00:11:22,413 --> 00:11:26,406
别烦恼了 Albert正在外面跑业务
But don't worry.Albert is out there doing the business.

159
00:11:26,493 --> 00:11:28,211
我们都会好起来的
We'll be all right.

160
00:11:28,973 --> 00:11:33,046
Katherine Winterborn是只超级怪物
Katherine Winterborn is an ogre of gargantuan amplitude.

161
00:11:33,973 --> 00:11:36,043
你仍认为她是我们的目标?
You still think she's our mark?

162
00:11:36,133 --> 00:11:38,249
她富有 她怀恨在心...
She's rich,she's bitter...

163
00:11:38,333 --> 00:11:41,689
只要用对了方法 她就会像蝴蝶一样展开
and with the right key,she'll open up like a butterfly.

164
00:11:41,773 --> 00:11:42,967
她有情人吗?
Any boyfriends?

165
00:11:43,053 --> 00:11:45,442
不 至少我们对其一无所知
No.At least none that we know of.

166
00:11:45,893 --> 00:11:48,327
那会像与尼罗河鳄鱼睡觉一样
That would be like sleeping with a Nile crocodile.

167
00:11:48,413 --> 00:11:50,563
好的 那么该你出场了
Well,there's your in,then.

168
00:11:50,973 --> 00:11:52,804
- 你这样想? - 我确定
- You think? - I know.

169
00:11:53,173 --> 00:11:54,526
用什么 性爱?
What,sex?

170
00:11:57,493 --> 00:11:59,484
等等 请等一下
Wait.Please,just a second.

171
00:11:59,573 --> 00:12:01,928
June对我来说意味着很多 我证实...
June means a lot to me.I proved that...

172
00:12:02,053 --> 00:12:03,964
不 不由你做 Albie
No,not you,Albie.

173
00:12:05,253 --> 00:12:07,892
你那样玷污你的贞操太不值了
You're far too precious to be sullied in that way.

174
00:12:07,973 --> 00:12:11,010
抱歉 把你的裤子穿好 我准备来硬的了
Sorry,put your trousers on.I'm ready and I'm bang up for it.

175
00:12:11,093 --> 00:12:15,769
不 我们不会让孩子来做男人的事 对吧 Michael?
No,we don't send boys to do a man's job.Right,Michael?

176
00:12:15,853 --> 00:12:16,888
不 我们不会
No,we do not.

177
00:12:16,973 --> 00:12:19,931
Mickey能施展他的魅力并且不脱下裤子
Mickey can spin his charm and still keep his trousers on.

178
00:12:20,013 --> 00:12:21,446
那是他伟大的天赋
It's his great gift.

179
00:12:21,533 --> 00:12:25,321
你两个回温泉旅馆去 尽你们所能收集所有的信息
You two go back to the spa,get every piece of information you can.

180
00:12:25,453 --> 00:12:27,683
我会安排和Katherine Winterborn见面
I'll arrange a meeting with Katherine Winterborn.

181
00:12:46,493 --> 00:12:49,530
- 我找Elliot先生 - 你是Winterborn夫人?
- I'm looking for Mr.Elliot. - Mrs.Winterborn?

182
00:12:49,613 --> 00:12:52,844
他让我告诉你 他在地平线休息室等你
He said to say to meet you in the Horizon Lounge.

183
00:12:53,773 --> 00:12:57,163
- 楼梯在哪里? - 那可是在40层 夫人
- Where are the stairs? - It's on the 40th floor,madam.

184
00:12:57,253 --> 00:12:59,608
电梯就在那边
The lifts are just through there.

185
00:13:40,533 --> 00:13:42,763
- 我听说电梯中间出了问题 - 什么?
- Problem with the middle lift,I hear. - Excuse me?

186
00:13:42,853 --> 00:13:46,812
我们接到责任经理报告说是左中央电梯出现颤抖
We got a report from the duty manager that the left central lift was juddering.

187
00:13:46,893 --> 00:13:48,724
我没听说过 我打电话问他
News to me.Let me call him.

188
00:13:48,813 --> 00:13:51,532
只需五分钟 我不能不管它
It'll take me five minutes.I can't just leave it.

189
00:13:51,613 --> 00:13:55,606
我要么修理它要么关掉它 对我来说这都一样 先生
Either I fix it or I shut it down.It's all the same to me,sir.

190
00:13:55,893 --> 00:13:57,963
- 去修吧 - 好的
- Go on. - All right.

191
00:14:24,933 --> 00:14:26,650
Winterborn夫人
Mrs.Winterborn.

192
00:14:27,198 --> 00:14:29,592
(抱歉 有个紧急会议 Andy Elliot)

193
00:14:53,711 --> 00:14:54,860
抱歉
Sorry.

194
00:15:04,391 --> 00:15:06,063
出什么事了?
What's happening?

195
00:15:08,991 --> 00:15:10,060
有人吗?
Hello?

196
00:15:10,151 --> 00:15:11,220
<i>抱歉 先生</i>
<i>Sorry about this,sir.</i>

197
00:15:11,311 --> 00:15:12,983
稍等一会儿就正常了
I'll have you moving in a while.

198
00:15:13,071 --> 00:15:16,347
请你快点 我开会要迟到了
Quick as you can,please.I'm late for a meeting.

199
00:15:16,431 --> 00:15:18,501
难道总是这样的?
Isn't that always the way?

200
00:15:19,791 --> 00:15:20,860
你还好吧?
Are you all right?

201
00:15:20,951 --> 00:15:24,739
不 我非常不喜欢这样 你能催他们快点吗?
No,I don't do lifts very well.Can you hurry them,please?

202
00:15:25,791 --> 00:15:28,908
注意 你能快点吗?这里面有位女士感觉不好了
Look,could you hurry it up?There's a lady in here feeling unwell.

203
00:15:28,991 --> 00:15:30,902
<i>好的 不会等太久的</i>
<i>Yeah,it shouldn't be too long now.</i>

204
00:15:31,431 --> 00:15:33,308
- 你在做什么? - 你很惊恐
- What are you doing? - You're panicking.

205
00:15:33,391 --> 00:15:37,589
看着我 看我的眼睛 什么事都别想 什么人也别想
Now look at me.Look into my eyes.Think of nothing and no one else.

206
00:15:38,191 --> 00:15:41,149
- 我要吐了 - 看着我 这里
- I'm going to be sick. - Look at me.Here.

207
00:15:41,431 --> 00:15:45,026
非常好 现在 想象一下 你在河边非常地镇静
Very good.Now,think,you're very calm.You're by a river bank.

208
00:15:45,111 --> 00:15:49,389
阳光照在河水的涟漪上 河水幽绿而凉爽
The sun is dappling the water.The water is dark green and very cool.

209
00:15:49,871 --> 00:15:52,624
微风拨动着流水 你听到了吗?
There's a breeze playing with the rushes.Can you hear it?

210
00:15:52,711 --> 00:15:54,269
好了?非常好
Yeah?Very good.

211
00:15:54,351 --> 00:15:59,061
你非常镇静地坐在岸边 用你的脚激起水花
You're very calm as you sit by the bank and splash your feet in the water.

212
00:15:59,471 --> 00:16:02,429
你能感觉到冰凉的河水从你脚上流过
Can you feel the cold water against your skin?

213
00:16:02,511 --> 00:16:03,580
非常好
Very good.

214
00:16:04,231 --> 00:16:05,744
我和责任经理谈过
I spoke to the duty manager.

215
00:16:05,831 --> 00:16:09,585
这位美国商人在纽约或芝加哥
There was this American businessman in New York.Or maybe it was Chicago.

216
00:16:09,671 --> 00:16:10,865
谁给你们公司打电话的?
Who called your company?

217
00:16:10,951 --> 00:16:14,148
他在一架电梯里全神贯注工作了三个小时 不通风 没有空调
He got stuck in a lift for three hours.No ventilation,no air con.

218
00:16:14,231 --> 00:16:17,860
最后当他们把他弄出来时 他的心脏像只易碎的包一样破了
When they finally got him out,his heart had exploded like a crisp packet.

219
00:16:17,951 --> 00:16:20,067
快点弄完
Just hurry up and finish.

220
00:16:20,151 --> 00:16:21,823
它很糟糕
Terrible,it was.

221
00:16:25,391 --> 00:16:26,460
我们在动
We're moving.

222
00:16:26,551 --> 00:16:29,190
是的 我们还好 我和你在一起
We are.We're okay.Stay with me.

223
00:16:29,991 --> 00:16:33,461
现在我们要站起来 好吗?你做的很好
Now we're gonna stand up,okay?You're doing very well.

224
00:16:33,671 --> 00:16:38,142
我们起来 非常镇静 吸气再呼气
Here we go.Very calm.Breathe in and out.

225
00:16:39,671 --> 00:16:41,309
做的很好
That's very good.

226
00:16:44,991 --> 00:16:47,585
- 你现在要好些吗? - 是的 谢谢
- You're gonna be all right now? - Yes,thank you.

227
00:16:47,671 --> 00:16:49,423
我想你该给这位女士道歉
I think you owe this lady an apology.

228
00:16:49,511 --> 00:16:51,581
至于我的事 如果我的钱有任何损失...
As far as I'm concerned,if I lose any money...

229
00:16:51,671 --> 00:16:54,583
因为我我开会迟到了 我会把帐单寄给你的
because I'm late for this meeting,I will send you the bill.

230
00:17:07,031 --> 00:17:08,669
你忘了这个
You forgot this.

231
00:17:10,191 --> 00:17:11,226
谢谢
Thank you.

232
00:17:11,311 --> 00:17:14,383
- 我完全应该谢谢你 - 不必客气 真的
- And I wanted to thank you properly. - There's no need,really.

233
00:17:14,471 --> 00:17:16,189
我喜欢你的河流
I liked your river.

234
00:17:16,591 --> 00:17:17,990
你的河流
Your river.

235
00:17:19,751 --> 00:17:21,389
现在 如果你再耽搁...
Now,if you'll excuse me...

236
00:17:21,471 --> 00:17:23,029
- 你开会迟到了 - 是的
- You're late for your meeting. - Yes.

237
00:17:23,111 --> 00:17:25,989
我能请你吃晚饭以表谢意吗?
Can I buy you dinner tonight as a thank-you?

238
00:17:28,311 --> 00:17:30,381
不胜欣喜
I'd be delighted.

239
00:17:32,471 --> 00:17:34,029
Patrick Greene
Patrick Greene.

240
00:17:36,271 --> 00:17:38,580
- 去开会吧 - 好的
- Now get to your meeting. - Yes.

241
00:17:50,151 --> 00:17:51,869
橘汁 冰
Orange juice.Ice.

242
00:17:53,471 --> 00:17:55,587
矿泉水冰块?
Mineral-water ice cubes?

243
00:17:56,231 --> 00:17:59,189
注意 我给你说过多少次了...
Look,how many times do I have to tell you people...

244
00:17:59,271 --> 00:18:01,262
我们再也别那样做了
we don't do that anymore.

245
00:18:01,351 --> 00:18:03,228
对不起 先生 我不知道
Sorry,sir,I didn't know.

246
00:18:03,311 --> 00:18:05,506
别让我再告诉你
Don't make me tell you again.

247
00:18:09,231 --> 00:18:10,869
那个不好意思
Sorry about that.

248
00:18:11,133 --> 00:18:14,330
你能想象那样?矿泉水冰块?
Can you imagine that?Mineral-water ice cubes?

249
00:18:14,413 --> 00:18:15,812
有点极端
A bit extreme.

250
00:18:15,893 --> 00:18:19,522
- 你在这里什么都好吧? - 非常好 什么都很完美
- Everything all right for you here? - Great.Everything's perfect.

251
00:18:19,613 --> 00:18:21,365
- 你是经理? - 不 我是业主
- You the manager? - No,I'm the owner.

252
00:18:21,453 --> 00:18:23,489
- Stephen Winterborn - Cindy Moore
- Stephen Winterborn. - Cindy Moore.

253
00:18:23,573 --> 00:18:25,962
- 你的旅馆真舒适 - 谢谢
- Lovely place you've got here. - Thank you.

254
00:18:26,053 --> 00:18:27,202
我是不是在某处读到过...
Didn't I read somewhere...

255
00:18:27,293 --> 00:18:29,648
你将把你的产业上市发行?
you're floating your business on the stock exchange?

256
00:18:29,733 --> 00:18:32,486
这个消息一定是你在金融报纸上读到的
You must read the very small print on the financial pages.

257
00:18:32,573 --> 00:18:33,688
是的
I do.

258
00:18:34,013 --> 00:18:35,924
是的 我们打算发行股票
Yeah,we're about to go public.

259
00:18:36,013 --> 00:18:37,412
真让人兴奋
Exciting.

260
00:18:37,653 --> 00:18:39,006
我希望是
I hope so.

261
00:18:39,093 --> 00:18:41,004
如果你不介意我想问问你是做什么的?
What do you do,if you don't mind me asking?

262
00:18:41,093 --> 00:18:42,128
我在这个城市工作
I work in the city.

263
00:18:42,213 --> 00:18:44,443
- 真的?做什么的? - Stephen
- Really?Doing what? - Stephen.

264
00:18:47,573 --> 00:18:50,371
- 很高兴认识你 Moore小姐 - 我也是
- Nice to meet you,Miss Moore. - Likewise.

265
00:18:50,813 --> 00:18:52,929
祝你股票上市好运
Good luck with the launch.

266
00:19:01,133 --> 00:19:03,089
- 你想要点什么? - 来杯马提尼
- What can I get you? - Dry martini.

267
00:19:03,173 --> 00:19:05,209
- 先生? - 你的蒸馏水从哪里来的?
- Sir? - Where's your still water from?

268
00:19:05,293 --> 00:19:07,761
- 英格兰 先生 - 英格兰哪里?
- England,sir. - Where in England?

269
00:19:09,013 --> 00:19:10,446
- 赫里福郡 - 那很不错
- Herefordshire. - That's fine.

270
00:19:10,533 --> 00:19:12,728
不要柠檬 两块矿泉水冰块
No lemon.Two mineral-water ice cubes.

271
00:19:12,813 --> 00:19:15,611
对不起 先生 我们只有一般的冰块
Sorry,sir,we only have regular ice cubes.

272
00:19:15,693 --> 00:19:19,322
从水里提炼出来的至少要7个人仔细检查的冰块
Made from water that has gone through at least seven human beings.

273
00:19:19,413 --> 00:19:21,131
不要冰 谢谢
No ice,thank you.

274
00:19:22,813 --> 00:19:25,168
- 你在香港做过什么? - 挣钱...
- What were you doing in Hong Kong? - Making money...

275
00:19:25,253 --> 00:19:28,370
观测台风从哪条路线登陆 直到香港被中国收回
seeing which way the wind would blow once the Chinese took it back.

276
00:19:28,453 --> 00:19:30,887
- 风往哪条路线吹? - 回到伦敦
- Which way is it blowing? - Back to London.

277
00:19:30,973 --> 00:19:34,682
你呢?除了在电梯里惊慌 你还做什么?
What about you?What do you do,apart from panic in lifts?

278
00:19:34,773 --> 00:19:37,287
- 你不知道我是谁? - 我应该知道?
- You don't know who I am? - Should I?

279
00:19:38,693 --> 00:19:41,082
这里的其他所有人都应该知道
Every other person in here would.

280
00:19:42,293 --> 00:19:45,603
我就是那个杀死前夫的狗的坏女人
I'm the evil bitch who killed her ex-husband's dog.

281
00:19:45,773 --> 00:19:47,491
我读到过
I read about that.

282
00:19:49,173 --> 00:19:51,209
媒体非常不喜欢你对吗?
The press didn't like you very much,did they?

283
00:19:51,293 --> 00:19:53,488
给点时间我会熬过来的
I'll get over it,given time.

284
00:19:53,573 --> 00:19:55,450
你现在就可以离开 我不会生气的
You can run away now.I won't be offended.

285
00:19:55,533 --> 00:19:58,286
我在这里很好 尽管这有些怪异
I'm fine where I am.It's funny though.

286
00:19:59,813 --> 00:20:04,125
- 你不想知道关于那条狗的事? - 如果你愿意就会告诉我
- Don't you want to know about the dog? - You'll tell me if you want to.

287
00:20:05,013 --> 00:20:07,527
打搅一下 先生 你们的晚餐准备好了
Excuse me,sir.Your table's ready.

288
00:20:07,813 --> 00:20:10,008
<i>你什么时候开始在温泉旅馆工作的</i>
<i>When did you start at the spa?</i>

289
00:20:10,613 --> 00:20:12,046
三个月前
Three months ago.

290
00:20:12,133 --> 00:20:14,522
- 你喜欢在那工作? - 还好
- Do you like it? - It's all right.

291
00:20:14,933 --> 00:20:18,403
你球打的不错 很有天分
You're pretty good with these balls.You're a natural.

292
00:20:18,493 --> 00:20:21,724
让我把球杆把手握稳点
Let me get just a nice firm grip on the end there.

293
00:20:22,093 --> 00:20:24,687
那么是谁先给你这份工作的?
So who got you in the job in the first place?

294
00:20:24,773 --> 00:20:27,003
让我把它打进去 准备好了?
Let me push it through.Ready?

295
00:20:28,733 --> 00:20:30,689
- 哇 - 一起打进的
- Wow. - Together.

296
00:20:32,293 --> 00:20:34,329
- 你问了许多问题 - 是吗?
- You ask a lot of questions. - Do I?

297
00:20:34,413 --> 00:20:37,086
- 我能问你一个问题吗? - 好的 随便问
- Can I ask you one? - Yeah,fire away.

298
00:20:37,173 --> 00:20:39,004
你在这里做什么?
What are you doing here?

299
00:20:39,093 --> 00:20:41,402
只是和你一起打台球
Just playing with balls with you.

300
00:20:42,853 --> 00:20:44,650
你姐姐在哪里?
Where is your sister?

301
00:20:45,253 --> 00:20:47,926
她和一些朋友在剧院
She's at the theater with some friends.

302
00:20:48,093 --> 00:20:49,924
- 真不好意思 - 为什么?
- That's a shame. - Why?

303
00:20:50,133 --> 00:20:52,931
她很漂亮 她可以和我们一起来的
She's pretty.She could have come with us.

304
00:20:53,013 --> 00:20:55,846
- 我们去哪里? - 去我那里
- Where are we going? - To my place.

305
00:21:00,533 --> 00:21:03,969
她想要的东西我给不了她 于是她找了某个能给她的人
She wanted things I couldn't give her.So she found someone who could.

306
00:21:04,053 --> 00:21:06,931
- 受伤了吧? - 是的 像刀割一样
- Hurts,doesn't it? - Yeah,like a razor.

307
00:21:07,013 --> 00:21:08,162
孩子如何?
Kids?

308
00:21:09,053 --> 00:21:12,204
在我成为她所期待的人之前她不会要孩子
She wouldn't have them until I'd become what she wanted.

309
00:21:12,293 --> 00:21:14,488
如果她求你 你还会要她回去吗?
Would you take her back if she asked?

310
00:21:14,573 --> 00:21:17,041
不 我永远也给不了她想要的
No,I could never give her the things that she wants.

311
00:21:17,133 --> 00:21:19,124
问题不在于此
That wasn't the question.

312
00:21:22,213 --> 00:21:24,727
你说过那很怪异 什么很怪异?
You said it was funny.What's funny?

313
00:21:25,573 --> 00:21:28,326
我告诉你我的私事 而你却说那很怪异
I told you about my business and you said it was funny.

