What about June?

509
00:33:44,693 --> 00:33:47,810
我们会想想办法 我们一直在想办法
We'll think of something.We always do.

510
00:34:13,413 --> 00:34:16,883
- 梦幻般的作爱 Ash? - 不 谢谢 Eddie
- Fancy a Slow Comfortable Screw,Ash? - No,thanks,Eddie.

511
00:34:32,293 --> 00:34:33,362
