I got a call by mistake from the hospital.

540
00:36:06,973 --> 00:36:08,691
什么时候?
What time was this?

541
00:36:09,413 --> 00:36:11,005
昨天深夜
Late last night.

542
00:37:26,933 --> 00:37:28,252
别走
Don't go.

543
00:37:29,853 --> 00:37:31,172
我得走了
I have to.

544
00:37:31,973 --> 00:37:34,203
我还没有签合同
I haven't signed the contract.

545
00:37:35,053 --> 00:37:37,009
你不需要签了
And you're not going to.

546
00:37:38,173 --> 00:37:39,845
你是什么意思 Patrick?
What do you mean,Patrick?

547
00:37:39,933 --> 00:37:42,572
这样做对你来说是不好的
It's just not the right thing for you to do.

548
00:37:43,213 --> 00:37:44,931
