I don't understand.

549
00:37:45,693 --> 00:37:47,126
相信我
Trust me on this.

550
00:37:47,293 --> 00:37:49,682
我们什么时候再见?
When am I going to see you again?

551
00:37:50,973 --> 00:37:53,965
Katherine 你再也不会见到我了
Katherine,you're never going to see me again.

552
00:37:55,253 --> 00:37:56,368
