Why?

553
00:37:56,773 --> 00:37:59,162
必须得这样
That's just the way it has to be.

554
00:37:59,653 --> 00:38:01,006
对不起
I'm sorry.

555
00:38:11,693 --> 00:38:13,888
我们这样结束了?
You're done with me,are you?

556
00:38:14,373 --> 00:38:18,161
愚笨 痛苦的女人 容易勾搭有利可图?
Stupid,bitter woman,good for a shag and a few quid?

557
00:38:22,853 --> 00:38:26,971
这里没有旅馆 Katherine 没有温泉 没有投资者
There is no hotel,Katherine.No spa,no investors.

558
00:38:27,213 --> 00:38:29,169
我也不叫Patrick
My name is not Patrick.

559
00:38:30,333 --> 00:38:33,564
我和我的同谋把你选中作可能的欺诈对象
Some associates and myself picked you out as a potential victim.

560
00:38:33,653 --> 00:38:37,362
你富有,愤怒,困惑,怀恨在心
You were rich,bitter,angry,obsessed.

561
00:38:38,453 --> 00:38:40,603
对你下手的时机已经成熟了
You were ripe to be plucked.

562
00:38:40,933 --> 00:38:42,571
你是骗子
You're a con man.

563
00:38:44,373 --> 00:38:48,048
但我不会让你成为我们的目标 我不会那样做
But I will not let you be our mark.I won't be a part of it.

564
00:38:59,559 --> 00:39:00,708
