we might hook him in that way.

597
00:40:26,039 --> 00:40:28,314
- 我不想把她卷进来 - 血腥的地狱 Mickey
- I don't want her involved. - Bloody hell,Mickey.

598
00:40:28,399 --> 00:40:31,709
一定还有些破绽 他内部的破绽
There must be something.A hole in his wall.

599
