- No. - Danny,we need you.

614
00:41:26,519 --> 00:41:29,317
如果你不能从这个女人那里得到些具体的...
If you can't get something concrete from this woman...

615
00:41:29,399 --> 00:41:31,594
整个计划就会失败
this whole thing falls down.

616
00:41:36,639 --> 00:41:37,992
